WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:12.751 --> 00:00:14.770
Nina Dølvik Brochmann:
We grew up believing

00:00:14.794 --> 00:00:17.947
that the hymen is a proof of virginity.

00:00:19.358 --> 00:00:21.227
But it turns out, we were wrong.

00:00:22.060 --> 00:00:23.465
What we discovered

00:00:23.489 --> 00:00:27.720
is that the popular story we're told
about female virginity

00:00:28.208 --> 00:00:31.740
is based on two anatomical myths.

00:00:33.374 --> 00:00:37.668
The truth has been known
in medical communities for over 100 years,

00:00:38.251 --> 00:00:44.322
yet somehow these two myths
continue to make life difficult

00:00:44.346 --> 00:00:46.262
for women around the world.

00:00:47.714 --> 00:00:50.814
Ellen Støkken Dahl:
The first myth is about blood.

00:00:51.457 --> 00:00:55.139
It tells us that the hymen
breaks and bleeds

00:00:55.163 --> 00:00:58.268
the first time a woman has vaginal sex.

00:00:59.040 --> 00:01:02.734
In other words, if there is no blood
on the sheets afterwards,

00:01:02.758 --> 00:01:05.639
then the woman was simply not a virgin.

00:01:06.959 --> 00:01:11.135
The second myth is a logical
consequence of the first.

00:01:11.861 --> 00:01:15.535
Since the hymen is thought
to break and bleed,

00:01:15.559 --> 00:01:19.266
people also believe
that it actually disappears

00:01:19.290 --> 00:01:24.885
or is in some way radically altered
during a woman's first intercourse.

00:01:26.037 --> 00:01:27.621
If that were true,

00:01:28.216 --> 00:01:33.969
one would easily be able to determine
if a woman is a virgin or not

00:01:33.993 --> 00:01:36.152
by examining her genitals,

00:01:36.176 --> 00:01:38.748
by doing a virginity check.

00:01:40.290 --> 00:01:42.094
NDB: So that's our two myths:

00:01:42.118 --> 00:01:43.765
virgins bleed,

00:01:43.789 --> 00:01:45.999
and hymens are lost forever.

00:01:47.301 --> 00:01:50.460
Now, this may sound
like a minor issue to you.

00:01:50.484 --> 00:01:52.080
Why should you care

00:01:52.104 --> 00:01:56.541
about an obscure little skin fold
on the female body?

00:01:57.823 --> 00:02:01.028
But the truth is,
this is about so much more

00:02:01.052 --> 00:02:03.893
than an anatomical misunderstanding.

00:02:05.186 --> 00:02:09.166
The myths about the hymen
have lived on for centuries

00:02:09.190 --> 00:02:11.578
because they have cultural significance.

00:02:12.536 --> 00:02:15.450
They have been used as a powerful tool

00:02:15.474 --> 00:02:18.687
in the effort to control women's sexuality

00:02:18.711 --> 00:02:23.254
in about every culture,
religion and historical decade.

00:02:24.705 --> 00:02:27.560
Women are still mistrusted,

00:02:28.049 --> 00:02:29.409
shamed,

00:02:29.433 --> 00:02:30.602
harmed

00:02:30.626 --> 00:02:34.123
and, in the worst cases,
subjected to honor killings

00:02:34.147 --> 00:02:37.004
if they don't bleed
on their wedding night.

00:02:38.488 --> 00:02:43.146
Other women are forced
through degrading virginity checks,

00:02:43.170 --> 00:02:46.051
simply to obtain a job,

00:02:46.592 --> 00:02:48.600
to save their reputation

00:02:48.624 --> 00:02:50.074
or to get married.

00:02:51.367 --> 00:02:53.280
ESD: Like in Indonesia,

00:02:53.304 --> 00:02:58.242
where women are systematically examined
to enter military service.

00:02:59.336 --> 00:03:02.923
After the Egyptian uprisings in 2011,

00:03:02.947 --> 00:03:08.227
a group of female protesters were forced
to undergo virginity checks

00:03:08.251 --> 00:03:09.673
by their military.

00:03:10.936 --> 00:03:15.879
In Oslo, doctors are examining
the hymens of young girls

00:03:15.903 --> 00:03:20.016
to reassure parents
that their children are not ruined.

00:03:20.625 --> 00:03:23.276
And sadly, the list goes on.

00:03:24.533 --> 00:03:29.826
Women are so afraid not to live up to
the myths about the hymen

00:03:29.850 --> 00:03:34.308
that they choose to use
different virginity quick fixes

00:03:34.332 --> 00:03:35.925
to assure a bleeding.

00:03:36.952 --> 00:03:38.856
That could be plastic surgery,

00:03:38.880 --> 00:03:40.579
known as "revirgination,"

00:03:40.968 --> 00:03:44.473
it could be vials of blood
poured on the sheets after sex

00:03:44.887 --> 00:03:48.208
or fake hymens bought online,

00:03:48.232 --> 00:03:50.065
complete with theater blood

00:03:50.089 --> 00:03:54.571
and a promise to "kiss your deep,
dark secret goodbye."

00:03:58.438 --> 00:04:02.798
NDB: By telling girls
that no deed can be kept secret,

00:04:03.555 --> 00:04:07.192
that their bodies
will reveal them no matter what,

00:04:07.905 --> 00:04:10.557
we have endowed them with fear.

00:04:12.070 --> 00:04:14.957
Girls are afraid of ruining themselves,

00:04:14.981 --> 00:04:16.765
either through sport,

00:04:16.789 --> 00:04:17.940
play,

00:04:17.964 --> 00:04:19.115
tampon use

00:04:19.139 --> 00:04:20.441
or a sexual activity.

00:04:21.656 --> 00:04:25.229
We have curtailed their opportunities
and their freedoms.

00:04:26.213 --> 00:04:29.698
It's time we put an end
to the virginity fraud.

00:04:30.282 --> 00:04:33.253
It's time we break the myths
about the hymen

00:04:33.277 --> 00:04:34.902
once and for all.

00:04:36.267 --> 00:04:38.364
ESD: We are medical students,

00:04:38.388 --> 00:04:40.256
sexual health workers

00:04:40.280 --> 00:04:43.780
and the authors
of "The Wonder Down Under."

00:04:43.804 --> 00:04:45.070
(Laughter)

00:04:45.598 --> 00:04:49.259
That's a popular science book
about the female genitals.

00:04:49.852 --> 00:04:52.692
And in our experience,
people seem to believe

00:04:52.716 --> 00:04:57.216
that the hymen is some kind of a seal
covering the vaginal opening.

00:04:58.161 --> 00:05:01.987
In Norwegian, it is even called
"the virgin membrane."

00:05:02.376 --> 00:05:05.385
And with this,
we picture something fragile,

00:05:05.409 --> 00:05:08.240
something easily destructible,

00:05:08.264 --> 00:05:10.087
something you can rip through,

00:05:10.738 --> 00:05:13.974
perhaps like a sheet of plastic wrapping.

00:05:15.045 --> 00:05:18.830
You may have wondered
why we brought a hula hoop onstage today.

00:05:19.838 --> 00:05:20.993
We'll show you.

00:05:23.466 --> 00:05:24.715
(Laughter)

00:05:27.096 --> 00:05:29.950
Now, it is very hard to hide

00:05:29.974 --> 00:05:32.397
that something has happened
to this hoop, right?

00:05:33.442 --> 00:05:36.644
It is different
before and after I punched it.

00:05:37.035 --> 00:05:39.010
The seal is broken,

00:05:39.586 --> 00:05:41.345
and unless we change the plastic,

00:05:41.369 --> 00:05:43.489
it won't get back to its intact state.

00:05:44.677 --> 00:05:48.958
So if we wanted to do a virginity check
on this hoop right here,

00:05:48.982 --> 00:05:50.242
right now,

00:05:50.266 --> 00:05:51.960
that would be very easy.

00:05:52.827 --> 00:05:58.295
It's easy to say that this hoop
is not a virgin anymore.

00:05:59.244 --> 00:06:00.520
(Laughter)

00:06:01.184 --> 00:06:04.605
NDB: But the hymen
is nothing like a piece of plastic

00:06:04.629 --> 00:06:06.635
you can wrap around your food,

00:06:06.659 --> 00:06:07.809
or a seal.

00:06:08.456 --> 00:06:09.656
In fact ...

00:06:12.435 --> 00:06:14.006
it's more like this --

00:06:14.609 --> 00:06:17.011
a scrunchie or a rubber band.

00:06:18.437 --> 00:06:23.481
The hymen is a rim of tissue
at the outer opening of the vagina.

00:06:24.103 --> 00:06:27.942
And usually, it has a doughnut
or a half-moon shape

00:06:28.422 --> 00:06:30.576
with a large, central hole.

00:06:31.855 --> 00:06:33.307
But this varies a lot,

00:06:33.331 --> 00:06:36.767
and sometimes hymens can have fringes,

00:06:36.791 --> 00:06:38.627
it can have several holes,

00:06:39.182 --> 00:06:41.667
or it can consist of lobes.

00:06:42.696 --> 00:06:47.469
In other words, hymens
naturally vary a lot in looks,

00:06:47.493 --> 00:06:51.810
and that is what makes it so hard
to do a virginity check.

00:06:53.614 --> 00:06:57.154
ESD: Now that we know a bit more
about the hymen's anatomy,

00:06:57.178 --> 00:06:59.640
it's time to get back to our two myths:

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:01.769
virgins bleed,

00:07:01.793 --> 00:07:04.196
hymens are lost forever.

00:07:05.224 --> 00:07:09.015
But the hymen doesn't
have to break at all.

00:07:09.685 --> 00:07:14.500
The hymen is like a scrunchie
in function as well as in looks.

00:07:15.165 --> 00:07:17.667
And you can stretch a scrunchie, right?

00:07:18.811 --> 00:07:19.961
(Laughter)

00:07:20.446 --> 00:07:22.611
You can stretch a hymen, too.

00:07:23.673 --> 00:07:26.653
In fact, it's very elastic.

00:07:28.467 --> 00:07:29.921
And for a lot of women,

00:07:29.945 --> 00:07:34.593
the hymen will be elastic enough
to handle a vaginal intercourse

00:07:34.617 --> 00:07:37.124
without sustaining any damage.

00:07:39.051 --> 00:07:44.076
For other women, the hymen may tear a bit
to make room for the penis,

00:07:44.752 --> 00:07:46.749
but that won't make it disappear.

00:07:47.262 --> 00:07:49.872
But it may look
a bit different from before.

00:07:50.356 --> 00:07:53.831
It naturally follows
that you can't examine the hymen

00:07:53.855 --> 00:07:55.688
to check for virginity status.

00:07:56.565 --> 00:08:00.539
This was noted over 100 years ago in 1906

00:08:00.563 --> 00:08:03.548
by the Norwegian doctor Marie Jeancet.

00:08:04.432 --> 00:08:08.069
She examined a middle-aged sex worker

00:08:09.014 --> 00:08:14.432
and concluded that her genitalia
were reminiscent of a teenage virgin.

00:08:15.663 --> 00:08:17.582
But that makes sense, right?

00:08:17.606 --> 00:08:21.746
Because if her hymen
was never damaged during sex,

00:08:21.770 --> 00:08:24.475
then what were we expecting to see?

00:08:26.025 --> 00:08:29.593
ESD: Since hymens come
in every shape and form,

00:08:30.098 --> 00:08:31.490
it is difficult to know

00:08:31.514 --> 00:08:36.705
if a dent or a fold in it is there
because of previous damage

00:08:36.729 --> 00:08:39.732
or if it's just a normal
anatomical variant.

00:08:41.275 --> 00:08:44.062
The absurdity of virgin testing

00:08:44.542 --> 00:08:50.679
is illustrated in a study
done on 36 pregnant teenagers.

00:08:51.821 --> 00:08:54.321
When doctors examined their hymens,

00:08:54.345 --> 00:08:57.602
they could only find
clear signs of penetration

00:08:57.626 --> 00:09:01.226
in two out of the 36 girls.

00:09:03.694 --> 00:09:08.241
So unless you believe
in 34 cases of virgin births --

00:09:08.265 --> 00:09:09.819
(Laughter)

00:09:10.288 --> 00:09:11.900
we must all agree

00:09:11.924 --> 00:09:16.143
that also our second myth
has taken a vital blow.

00:09:17.258 --> 00:09:20.648
You simply cannot look a woman
between her legs

00:09:20.672 --> 00:09:22.819
and read her sexual story.

00:09:27.813 --> 00:09:32.195
NDB: Like most myths,
the myths about the hymen are untrue.

00:09:33.391 --> 00:09:38.910
There is no virgin seal
that magically disappears after sex,

00:09:38.934 --> 00:09:43.981
and half of virgins
can easily have sex without bleeding.

00:09:45.583 --> 00:09:48.912
We wish we could say
that by removing these myths,

00:09:48.936 --> 00:09:50.619
everything would be OK,

00:09:51.187 --> 00:09:56.293
that shame, harm and honor killings
would all just disappear.

00:09:57.746 --> 00:09:59.993
But of course, it's not that simple.

00:10:00.602 --> 00:10:04.215
Sexual oppression of women
comes from something much deeper

00:10:04.239 --> 00:10:10.148
than a simple anatomical misunderstanding
about the properties of the hymen.

00:10:11.231 --> 00:10:16.590
It's a question of cultural and religious
control of women's sexuality.

00:10:16.993 --> 00:10:19.323
And that is much harder to change.

00:10:20.203 --> 00:10:21.729
But we must try.

00:10:23.725 --> 00:10:27.963
ESD: As medical professionals,
this is our contribution.

00:10:29.014 --> 00:10:33.537
We want every girl, parent
and [future] husband to know

00:10:33.561 --> 00:10:37.393
what the hymen is and how it works.

00:10:38.103 --> 00:10:39.377
We want them to know

00:10:39.401 --> 00:10:43.249
that the hymen can't be used
as a proof of virginity.

00:10:44.344 --> 00:10:48.941
And that way, we can remove
one of the most powerful tools

00:10:48.965 --> 00:10:51.432
used to control young women today.

00:10:53.673 --> 00:10:55.604
After telling you this,

00:10:56.490 --> 00:10:59.466
you may wonder what the alternative is,

00:11:00.734 --> 00:11:05.005
for if we cannot use the hymen
as a proof of virginity for women,

00:11:05.470 --> 00:11:07.100
then what should we use?

00:11:09.631 --> 00:11:12.371
We opt for using nothing.

00:11:12.885 --> 00:11:14.863
(Cheering)

00:11:14.887 --> 00:11:16.048
If you --

00:11:16.072 --> 00:11:20.096
(Applause)

00:11:22.326 --> 00:11:26.406
If you really want to know
if a woman is a virgin or not,

00:11:26.785 --> 00:11:27.939
ask her.

00:11:27.963 --> 00:11:29.113
(Laughter)

00:11:29.449 --> 00:11:34.046
But how she answers
that question is her choice.

00:11:35.771 --> 00:11:36.922
Thank you.

00:11:36.946 --> 00:11:39.314
(Applause)

